overview: On April 1st the stars of JCW and LA Fights do battle at The Collective live on FITE straight from Fair Park in Dallas, TX. First of the matches in the lineup are already announced, here they are:  Sandra Moon vs Billie Starkz  B-Boy vs Grim Reefer  Jack Cartwheel vs Alec Price  Big Vin vs Juicy Finau  Dark Sheik vs Charles Mason  Cole Radrick vs Kevin Blackwood  Marcus Mathers vs Nick Wayne  Super Series of Survivals Elimination Match  Team JCW (Bam Sullivan, Charlie Tiger, Ellis Taylor, Janai Kai, Jordan Oliver, SLADE & Yoya) vs Team LA Fights
title: LA Fights Vs JCW
